        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer510053065" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1551623468207838821">Extremely solid story collection by Grant, the chief purveyor of &quot;quiet horror.&quot; Necessary for Oxrun Station completists because there are three Oxrun stories that are difficult to find elsewhere. You are not going to find a lot of grue here unless it drives the plot and don&apos;t always expect a King-like resolution of everything at the end. Some ambiguity is the norm.</span>
  <span id="freeText1551623468207838821" style="display:none">Extremely solid story collection by Grant, the chief purveyor of "quiet horror." Necessary for Oxrun Station completists because there are three Oxrun stories that are difficult to find elsewhere. You are not going to find a lot of grue here unless it drives the plot and don't always expect a King-like resolution of everything at the end. Some ambiguity is the norm.</span>
  <a data-text-id="1551623468207838821" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
